	<h2>Motor Vehicle Gateway Tips</h2>
        <p><b>The Motor Vehicle Gateway search provides access to real-time motor vehicle registration information from approximately 43 states. Search for data on registrants, owners and lien holders of a vehicle. No historical records will be included, only current information will be returned.</b></p>
        <p>&nbsp;<br>Find a vehicle record using one or more of the following search techniques:<br>&nbsp;</p>
        <ol id="font81">
          <li>Search using a VIN. The Vehicle Identification Number generally consists of seventeen characters that are used to uniquely identify a motor vehicle.<br><br></li>
          <li>Search using the vehicle's Tag Number and State.<br><br></li>
          <li>Search by an individual's Name, Street Address, City, and State or Name, Street Address, and Zip.<br><br></li>
          <li>Name, Street Address, City and State, Year, Make, and Model of Vehicle.  Note: The Make and Model drop-lists are not available until you enter a Year.<br><br></li>
        </ol>
